<item>
            <title>[HIVE-1878] Set the version of Hive trunk to &apos;0.7.0-SNAPSHOT&apos; to avoid confusing it with a release</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-1878</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The build.properties file currently sets version=0.7.0, which results in artifacts named&lt;br/&gt;
hive-xxx-0.7.0.jar and a tarball with the name hive-0.7.0.tar.gz. Only the actual 0.7.0 release&lt;br/&gt;
should generate JARs and tarballs with this name.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12494560">HIVE-1878</key>
            <summary>Set the version of Hive trunk to &apos;0.7.0-SNAPSHOT&apos; to avoid confusing it with a release</summary>
